task.summary: Async close test was added. Base exception was changed to IOException.
[open] method was fixed and correctly applied in test.
Cluster allocation strategy was isolated in interface. Concurrency problem with [freeClusterCount] was found and fixed.
DtaEntry was removed. Self-reference root folder was supported.
Folder content reading procedure was implemented.
Read file channel implementation. Root folder test read.
Memory map problem localized and fixed..
Prepare storage for root record in header. Old solutions are the best!
Dirty status support was changed to be consistent with FS transactions.
Delete test is implemented. Fix delete procedures.
Transaction gap was fixed in folder creation.
Test set was splitted to WR and Tree structure parts.
Lost write problem was resolved. The APPEND mode was specified and supported.
FATFile[] listFiles() was implemented for folder.
Deleted record storage procedure was changed.
Dump was fixed from escape seq. The name of root folder was changed.
Recycable collection for FATFile and FATFolder were implemented. Several problem were resolved. Java doc was updated.
RC1: Code cleanup, performance degradation on delete was fixed. [Force] in any context is extrimly slow.
RC1.1: Funny test was added. LastModyfy change calls for read were removed.
